title: NxGTR Arcade Car Racing 3D Patch 06-11
description:
This file is related to the torrent at: http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/8558194/NxGTR_Arcade_Car_Racing_3D_[Unreleased]

The servers were modified, so you will get an outdated warning using the other torrent, this is NOT the full game, only the updated executables.
